Nehemia olemo ni Jerusalem


1  Magi e weche mag Nehemia wuod Hakalia:

E due mar Kislev, e higa mar piero ariyo mar loch Artaxerxes, kane en Susa, dala ruoth, 
2  Hanani ma owadwa nobiro gi jomoko koa Juda. Napenjogi wach Jerusalem, kod wach jo-Yahudi mane odong’ kuom joma nodok kuno, koa e tuech Babulon, kuma nosetergie. 
3  Ne gidwoka niya, “Joma nodong’ e pinyno, koa e tuech koro oneno thagruok gi wich kuot maduong’. Ohinga mar Jerusalem osemuki, kendo dhorangeyene duto osewang’ gi mach.”


4  Kane awinjo wachno, nabet piny maywak kuom ndalo mogwarore, ka atueyo chiemo, kendo alemo e nyim Nyasach polo. 
5  Ne alemo kama: “A Ruoth Nyasaye ma Nyasach polo, Nyasaye maduong’ kendo malich. Irito singruok mitimo gi joma oheri kendo marito chikeni, kiherogi gi hera mosiko. 
6  Yie ichik iti kendo inen, mondo iwinj kwayona ma aketo e nyimi odiechieng’ gotieno, kakwayo ni jo-Israel. Ahulo richo ma wan jo-Israel wasetimo e nyimi. Ee, an kaachiel gi dhoodwa wasetimo richo. 
7  Wasekethoni adier, kendo ok waserito chike duto mane imiyo Musa jatichni. 
8  

To yie ipar gima ninyise, kiwacho niya, ‘Kuketho chikna, to anakeu e kind ogendini. 
9  

To kuduogo ira, mi urito chikna, to anachoku, kendo anadwoku e dala miseyiero mondo nyinga obedie, kata obedo ni uke muchopo e tung’ piny gi tung’ piny.’ 
10  A Ruoth Nyasaye, jo-Israel gin jotichni kendo jogo misewaro gi tekoni kod badi motegno. 
11  Yie ichik iti mondo iwinj kwayona kod kwayo jotichni mohero luoro nyingi, kendo yie iguedha kawuononi, mondo imi jal matiyone ogena.” E kindeno ne an jagam divai mar ruoth Artaxerxes.

